## About US

We are a duly registered company in Uganda with a both physical and remote 24hr open working office environment.

Cashleo Ltd is here to offer a seamless yet an easy and secure way individuals and SMEs to receive payments and transact online. We are working with a great deal of partners both directly and indirectly to bring you a simple way to process online payments. 

We are a team of young, passionate and energetic Ugandans with big aspirations to bring change and empower individuals and businesses in our society through technology.

Being a growing team with a strong technological background, ethical, passionaite and integrity, we pride ourselves in being the change we want to see and through building tools that empower and enable businesses, we are assured to see this come true.

Our works have appeared and been mentioned is popular news and technological channels such a WordPress, WordCamp, WordPressTV, WooCommerce, NewYork Magazine, One Young World.

Our goal is to see that every individual and SME has an easy and efficient way to receive and make online payments in both urban and rural areas seamlessly.

**Vision:**
To be the leading mobile and online payments provider in Uganda & Africa.

**Mission:**
To empower as many individuals, startups and small medium enterprises as possible and become the market leader for fast, secure and reliable payments in Uganda and Africa


