## Pricing

Our pricing is very simple. We don’t charge you until you make a transaction.

**Pay IN Transactions (Receive money)**
Momo payments, we charge 2.5% per transaction
Minimum PayIn UGX500 and NO maximum pay in ie (You’re not restricted on how much you can receive)

**Pay Out Transactions (Withdraw money)**
Minimum payout is 1000 UGX
Max daily payout is 1,000,000 UGX (subject to update upon request)

**Service				      Currency	      Charge**
Mobile Money Collection 	(UGX) 		   2.5%
Mobile Money Payout 	      (UGX)		      1,000
Liquidation 			      (UGX)		      20,000
Visa Collection			   (ALL)		      5%
SMS				            (UGX)	      	50

